data.description:
This spacious early 1900's home has been meticulously maintained for the last 25 years. The property had a new roof installed in September 2023. A new hot water heater in July of 2023 and a new AC in April of 2023. 
It has 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom upstairs. A fourth bedroom and bathroom downstairs. The house has a large family room that was added on. Its perfect for a large family Christmas around the fireplace. It also has a formal dining room with a table that seats 8.  Also the property has alley driveway access and an oversized 2 car attached garage! 
With plenty or storage space.  This home has been filled with lovely family memories and is ready for more!
